description: I got a call from a young and very shy Slovakian boy. At least he was shy on the phone, the reality was quite different. He needed 20 000 Crowns to get through a period of unemployment. He also had to pay bills for a car repair. The guy almost ran over a girl. He evaded her at the last moment but crashed his car. I guess, he could had been in much more serious trouble than he was. Not even I would be able to get him out of prison. 20 000 was not that much so I quickly made him my generous proposition. He was a bit stunned, I could see his face turning red. He was definitely embarrassed but easy money was more tempting. I was extremely horny so I fucked him all over his apartment. We even almost broke his table
title: Debt Dandy 220
